{"type": "article", "id": 13500, "title": "Witu“Cosmos” 系列包袋", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-14T07:46:05Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 41, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000259u6MvB9scpfinhOLR.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t来自墨尔本的 Witu 推出全新 “Cosmos” 系列包袋，材料全部使用潜水衣物料，打造出手拿包，水桶包，大 Tote 等，看上去质感非常特别。其中，经典款 Habitat Bucket Bag 推出了新的大地色系，各种印花看上去有也冲击力十足。 其中有一款水桶包比起市面上现有的水桶包，看上去更加特别。而适合笔记本电脑大小的背包，也兼具实用性和美观。这是<a href=\"http://www.witu.com.au/#!cosmos/c180v\" target=\"_blank\">购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141249i3Bv8xYtezalQJuA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50093809\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261412496irJsBwyFUmR7Nvh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50093809\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141250wHiyaudtgRVNjA34.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50093809\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141250h10BNQCe3ZAdPUMo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50093809\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141251UzdpGgc0jOWHV93T.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50093809\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141251BvleSwVnK7mdo1YU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50093809\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141252eCp9ait4DNc5wuyT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50093809\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141252tPXFR407rawcgDO3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50093809\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}